-- Vontobel Won’t Abandon BB Biotech Bid, SonntagsZeitung Reports
-- B y   L e i g h   B a l d w i n
-- 2012-07-22T08:31:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-22/vontobel-won-t-abandon-bb-biotech-bid-sonntagszeitung-reports.html
Vontobel Holding AG (VONN)  will persist
with its bid to buy  BB Biotech AG (BION)  after an initial offer was
rejected,  SonntagsZeitung  reported, citing Vontobel’s head of
corporate finance Hanspeter Gehrer.  BB Biotech shareholders in Switzerland and abroad have
encouraged Vontobel to continue pursuing the takeover, the Swiss
newspaper quoted Gehrer as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Leigh Baldwin in Zurich at 
 lbaldwin3@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
